snippet: Rio de Janeiro will not keep its promise of cleaning polluted Guanabara Bay for the 2016 Olympics, Mayor Eduardo Paes said on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Mayor: Rio Will Fail to Keep Pledge to Clean Bay
headline.main: Mayor: Rio Will Fail to Keep Pledge to Clean Bay

lead_paragraph: Rio de Janeiro will not keep its promise of cleaning polluted Guanabara Bay for the 2016 Olympics, Mayor Eduardo Paes said on Saturday.
